---
title: Mediterranean Orzo and Chicken Tenders Salad with Bocconcini and Oregano
description: Orzo gets a Grecian makeover! Al dente orzo is tossed with chicken, olives, salty feta, tomatoes, spinach and fresh bocconcini for a delicious combination of Italian and Greek flavours!
